# Stage1-Core transport for the Issue #23 native acceptance image.
#
# Every pair is PACKED_LITTLE_ENDIAN_WORD followed by BYTE_COUNT. Words contain
# at most six bytes, so they are exact Kofun Int values. The verifier only
# transports these Kofun-authored ELF/header/instruction bytes into a file.
#
# The image has separate RX and RW PT_LOAD segments. Its code checks every raw
# open, write, lseek, read, and close return. Any negative return, short IO, or
# byte mismatch exits 1. Only the fully verified path prints the success line
# and exits 0.

